      },
      "writtenOn": "2022-01-10T09:11:05Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I wasn\u0027t really convinced before trying to implement it, having the meaning of |i| depending on the return value of the function, but in the end it turned out way better than I thought. The code is simpler this way, and I think it\u0027s not too hard to read.",
