      "writtenOn": "2022-01-07T21:59:11Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "i don\u0027t think we need to maintain ordering.  find the last entry in the array and swap with that.\n\n for (last \u003d i; envp[last]; ++last)\n   continue;\n --last;\n envp[i] \u003d envp[last];\n envp[last] \u003d NULL;\n\nworks even if i \u003d\u003d last",
      "revId": "3f2eed4258edfc30e2c1190f144d8ff370a0413c",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889"
    },
    {
