      "writtenOn": "2022-01-10T09:11:05Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The only drawback I can think of, is for weird/invalid envs with duplicate variable names, where we would possibly alter the behaviour of the app we\u0027re launching, as we wouldn\u0027t maintain the ordering. It\u0027s probably negligible, though. I implemented it as you suggested.",
